Explore a richly detailed world<br>-Befriend the townsfolk<br>-Learn seven skills: Farming, Forestry, Mining, Fishing, Combat, Stealth and Magic!<br>-Have cute pets and take care of them<br>-Plumb the depths of vast dungeons<br>-Create useful machines and cook food<br>-Play many Mini-games and solve puzzles<br>-Use magic equipment to offer special bonuses<br>-Learn lore and secrets from in-game books<br>-Witness the changing seasons and dynamic world<br>-Attend the town festivals through the year<br>-Over an hour of OST!<br>-Collect various items to unlock sweet bonuses around town<br>-Uncover the many secrets of Spellfield...",
